metadata.name: OtherShit Portal Card (1/209)
metadata.description:
Welcome to The OtherShit.  
This special card looks great on your wallet. 
And who knows what else can come from/through it... specially if you put it next to a Shitty Shitcoins NFT.  
In the end, this card is a Portal to The OtherShit.  
Only 209 Special Editions of this Card will ever exist. 
The 1 that makes the 210 is the 1/1 available at Shitty Shitcoins Official NFT collection.
